    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In VariDungeon, you are a hero exploring a dungeon. It may sound classic, but each run is different because its structure changes every time you start again ! Power-ups, enemies, bosses, traps, ... You need to adapt to all these elements in order to defeat the final boss and save the King !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gorgeous pixel-art graphics in the style of Game Boy </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 playable classes </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >69 enemies and traps that get stronger as you so </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25 power-ups to combine in order to win each fight </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 bosses trying to kill you </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >more than 250 rooms </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More environments, enemies, power-ups, playable characters and bosses to come in themed updates !</p></li></ul>",
